                    <description>&lt;p&gt;org.apache.hadoop.hbase.HColumnDescriptor.isLegalFamilyName(byte[]) accesses byte&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; w/o first checking the array length.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
